# Clean Code - Comments

## Avoid explanatory comments

Do not add comments whose only purpose is to explain what a block of code, condition, variable, or function is doing.

Bad example:

```ts
if (created.ok) {
  // Only refresh if the link was created successfully.
  await refreshLinked();
}